reviews.text: Despite being a medium-sized restaurant, there is no lavatory. Staff advise customers to use the McDonald's toilet next door! Menus are Chinese-only. Chicken wings were dry, and service was average. There is tea and a stack of cups for self-service on each table. No napkins provided.
Convenient location and transportation, stable food quality.
high c/p value
fast ... taste ok la

Very mixed feeling about this local restaurant. Vibe and environment is average or slightly below, staff politeness is non-existent, but BBQ meat here is really good. Fatty char siew, roast duck and chicken are all way above average. Plus it opens late (or 24 I'm not sure) and all taxi drivers would come for supper.

p.s. parking outside on the road would often gets fined but the restaurant does alert patrons

reviews.text: 太度差得很、價錢全屯門最貴、服務員最差
新輝記屬於垃圾級食店，試過幾次在早上點三文治，麵包不新鮮、有異味、可能已發霉；湯麵比我自己煮的還要差，至於服務員的水平就無謂多說；如果閣下唔介意做白老鼠就隨便光顧。
態度差，難食！所有野都做到油淋淋! 同的士司機講開，連佢地都唔會過黎食，所以已經由以前開24小時變成深夜收舖，即係冇客啦！
味道一般，衛生不太好，但勝在24小時營業
方便夜班一族，至零晨有開至半夜

reviews.text: Vast selection of baby related merchandise, Parents favorite. A huge supermarket sits next to this department store as well. A true one stop shop for families
Huge mall, connected to other shopping as well.  Good transportation options in and out.
Great place for shopping, especially for beauty products! Family mall with everything you need.

Central location. Linked to 5 or 6 other shopping arcades. Linked to the subway line at Tuen Mun station. Many car parks, and some offer free parking with purchase. I'm happy with this place as I'm always able to find whatever I'm looking for here. Finding my car after getting parking ticket stamped is always a challenge tho.
This is the closest to home and what you get.ftom.anywhere, you get it here  mostly, why ho anywhere else. My kids are practical, when they are here, they love it just here.
